summary:
We Wish You A Metal Christmas

 

And a headbanging new year. I saw the Aggretsuko Christmas Special, and... Eh. Retsuko becomes...
caption:
We Wish You A Metal Christmas

And a headbanging new year.

I saw the Aggretsuko Christmas Special, and…

Eh.

Retsuko becomes a bit of a harlot, so that’s a thing. Fenneko is fine, Haida’s still his depressed jumpy try-hard self, and everything else…

Eh.

It wasn’t bad, I just think the previous episodes were of higher quality.
Oh well. At least Retsuko’s outfit looks good. Bearpaw boots are fun to draw.
